# Playwright Coverage

- For every new user-facing feature or regression fix, add or update a Playwright test in `tests/e2e/`.
- Start from `tests/e2e/TEMPLATE.spec.ts` when creating a new feature spec.
- Reuse shared helpers from `tests/e2e/helpers/` before duplicating setup logic.
- Prefer stable locators such as labels, roles, and `data-testid` hooks over brittle CSS selectors.
- If a feature intentionally ships without Playwright coverage, explain why in the final handoff.
